{"tid":1531274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(英文文宣) Schedule for the upcoming protest schedule","createTime":"2019-09-02T07:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T02:26:03.000Z","uid":36471,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ddb2e207769c3cdd00eda05202f7a9c5e1b7582c","tid":1531274,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:22:13.000Z","msg":"小弟英文廢，有錯請指正<br />\n<br />\nHi all, here is the most updated schedule for the upcoming protests.  If you are planning to visit Hong Kong soon, please plan ahead for potential traffic delays.  We are sorry for any inconvenience caused! <br />\n<br />\n7 September：<br />\nUS currency withdrawal day (to give pressure on the Hong Kong financial system)<br />\nTime: Anytime <br />\nVenue: Any bank in Hong Kong <br />\n<br />\n8 September :<br />\nParade in support of the advancement of &quot;Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act&quot;<br />\nTime: TBC<br />\nVenue: TBC<br />\n<br />\n13 September :<br />\n&quot;Flowers blooming everywhere&quot; on the Mid-Autumn Festival<br />\nTime: TBC<br />\nVenue: TBC (most probably be held in different districts at the same time)<br />\n<br />\n14 September :<br />\nThe Fireflies of Bauhinia - Secondary Students Assembly<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E5%87%9D%E7%81%AB%E4%B9%8B%E8%81%B2-Youthire-100210034691251/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E5%2587%259D%25E7%2581%25AB%25E4%25B9%258B%25E8%2581%25B2-Youthire-100210034691251%2F&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR22ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=674c5db8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E5%87%9D%E7%81%AB%E4%B9%8B%E8%81%B2-Youthire-100210034691251/</a><br />\nOrganizer: 凝火之聲 Youthire（Applying for the letter for no-objection from the popo）<br />\nTime: 16:00 - 21:00<br />\nVenue: Temple Mall, Wong Tai Sin<br />\n<br />\n15 September :<br />\nTBD<br />\n<br />\n22 September :<br />\nTBD<br />\n<br />\n29 September :<br />\nGlobal Assembly to fight against #Chinazi <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1511138/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1511138/page/1</a><br />\nTime: Open for discussion<br />\nVenue: Open for discussion<br />\n<br />\n1 October：<br />\nTBD, but definitely something will happen on that day<br />\n<br />\nWe understand that most of you will not be able to comment on LIHKG, but please feel free to ask us any questions on reddit, twitter or facebook should you need further clarification!  Thank you for your support!"},{"pid":"8aa2ed3112b5d4190370705adb08dbb8abccf072","tid":1531274,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:23:07.000Z","msg":"Push 1/10"},{"pid":"6f5aaac07f98a04ca3a12759c8a42cd0b8f16a7c","tid":1531274,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7b810322168b1d7a2621ea2f711e3dcc863a70","tid":1531274,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"大量文宣推<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人權法</strong></span><br />\n請瘋狂tweet and retweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/brDxztB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbrDxztB.png&h=cf2043ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wy4wP1